text: Novoakbashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Starogumerovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 54 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 32 km from Kushnarenkovo, 2 km from Starogumerovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Novoakbashevo
